On the Village team will be a Harlot (who can check to see if someone visited their target each night), a Stalker (can check to see if their target visited someone last night), a Protector (can prevent someone being killed each night, can't protect the same person two nights in a row), a Tarot Reader (once per game, can find out what roles were alive that night) and two vanilla villagers.
